The course deepens the knowledge of Estonian stylistics. The course develops the sense of style, teaches writing different types of texts, improves the knowledge of orthography and interpunctuation rules.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to train the students to produce various stylistically and functionally appropriate  written texts ; to introduce the principles of documentation.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After completing the course the student: * knows different types of texts;   * can write stylistically appropriate texts; * can compile and formalise business letters
